I replied that obviously you are aware of an incorrect price on the app but still have that uber partnership and that pricing. I am very impressed by the Doggie Water Fountain right outside the store. It's flowing fresh water! 🐶 Not just an ordinary water dish. I have never seen something like this before. This is so much more appealing for the dogs and their humans. 🐕 🐩🐾🐾 This says to me that the shop considers itself to be part of the neighborhood. 🏘️Not only serving human customers, but being considerate of their canine companions, as well! 🐾🐾😊💖 They also have bicycle-turned-flower-garden across on 10th Street. 🚲🌺 It's an old bicycle with the store's logo on the side and the front basket transformed into a mini garden. It beautifies the neighborhood and is an eye-catching advertising piece for passing people. Earlier this year, the store was also growing some of it's own basil -- or was it oregano? -- in the bicycle basket planter. They have a windowbox planter in front of the store, also with fresh herbs and flowers. What else would they be doing with those delicious fresh herbs, but using them for delicious pizza! 🍕😊💕
